<% content_for :title do %>
	Pay per click advertising campaign management services Hyderabad, Bangalore
<% end %>
<% content_for :meta_tags do %>
	<meta name="description" content="Maximize your ROI with WebEnrich Pay per Click (PPC) advertising management services; run by Google Adwords certified Pay per Click (PPC) professionals from Vizag, Hyderabad, Bangalore India.">
	<meta name="keywords" content="PPC Services, PPC India, PPC Management, search engine marketing, PPC Services India, bid management, ppc company, ppc agency, ppc consultant, ppc consulting, ppc firms, Google Adwords, Vizag, Hyderabad, Bangalore India">
<% end %>
<div class="services-page">
	<div class="mobile-page-main mobile-page-inner">
		<div class="main-title">
			<div class="container">
				<h1>
					<%= link_to online_marketing_path, :class => 'left' do %>
						<%= image_tag image_path('mobile/back-arrow.png') %>
					<% end %>
					Pay Per Click
				</h1>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="title-content">
				<div class="services-img services-inner-img">
					<%= image_tag image_path('mobile/ppc-icon.png'), alt: 'services-inner-img' %>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="services-text">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="ppc-content">
				<p>
					PPC is one of the popular internet marketing strategies that involves posting an advertisement on the pages of a search engine or on its network websites. The advertisement gets displayed when the visitor searches for a specific keyword or keywords. The advertiser pays only when the visitor clicks on the ad. Once the visitor clicks on the ad he is directed to the landing page.
				</p>
				<article>
					Today PPC is one of the most popular methods of introducing a product in the market. While it's true you should always be optimizing your website to rank well in organic searches, PPC can yield valuable insights that help your business better position its online marketing.
				</article>
				<%= link_to "Continue Reading", '#', :class => 'waves-effect waves-light btn hide' %>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="container">
		<div class="services-text services-inner-content">
			<div class="online-ppc">
				<h2>What is PPC?</h2>
				<p>PPC is one of the popular internet marketing strategies that involves posting an advertisement on the pages of a search engine or on its network websites. The advertisement gets displayed when the visitor searches for a specific keyword or keywords. The advertiser pays only when the visitor clicks on the ad. Once the visitor clicks on the ad he is directed to the landing page.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="online-ppc">
				<h2>Why PPC?</h2>
				<p>Today PPC is one of the most popular methods of introducing a product in the market. While it's true you should always be optimizing your website to rank well in organic searches, PPC can yield valuable insights that help your business better position its online marketing.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="online-ppc">
				<h2>Why WebEnrich?</h2>
				<p>WebEnrich doesn't lose the forest for trees. We are different from many other businesses that blindly invest in PPC campaigns without realizing the role of SEO in the campaigns. WebEnrich designs and offers a perfect blend of SEO and PPC that not only drives quality traffic to your site but also supports your other marketing efforts.</p>
				<p>Our Google certified PPC experts closely follow your business needs, your target audience and industry trends to optimize your PPC campaigns appropriately. We back our propositions and recommendations with thorough research and truth be told, we are quite good in understanding the Google psyche.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="online-ppc">
				<h2>Lowest Cost Per Click</h2>
				<p>We understand that good advertisers get their due from Google, when your clicks become cheaper and your profit per click higher. That's where the services of WebEnrich your loyal PPC manager come in.</p>
			</div>
		</div>	
	</div>
	<div class="container">
		<div class="card ppc-services">
			<div class="card-content">
				<h2>Services In PPC Campaign</h2>
				<ul class="collection">
					<li class="collection-item">Keyword analysis.</li>
					<li class="collection-item">Strategic planning.</li>
					<li class="collection-item">Competitive evaluation and effective ad copy.</li>
					<li class="collection-item">Design and Development of landing pages and micro-sites so as to enhance the efficiency of your campaign.</li>
					<li class="collection-item">Profitability analysis, monitoring and campaign management.</li>
					<li class="collection-item">Tracking the performance of your ads, monitoring your budgets and keyword conversion rates.</li>
					<li class="collection-item">Split-test and tweaking your ad copy if necessary.</li>
				</ul>
				<p><%= link_to 'Contact', contact_us_path %> us to know more about our extensive PPC services.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="list-of-services list-of-detail-services">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="list-of-services-inner">
				<h1>Online marketing</h1>
				<div class="card">
					<ul>
						<li>
							<%= link_to search_engine_optimization_path do %>
								<strong>Search Engine Optimization</strong>
							<% end %>
						</li>
						<li>
							<%= link_to social_media_marketing_path do %>
								<strong>Social Media Marketing</strong>
							<% end %>
						</li>
						<li>
							<%= link_to email_marketing_path do %>
								<strong>Email Marketing</strong>
							<% end %>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>	
		</div>
	</div>
<!-- Our Clients -->
	<%= render 'layouts/widgets/our_clients' %>
<!-- start-project -->	
	<%= render 'layouts/widgets/start_project' %>
</div>